==English==

==''Adj''.==

*1. (''Colloq'') Having the necessary knack, personality and instinct for survival in rough, urban environments.

*2. (''Colloq'') Possessing a style that embodies the life and microculture located within urban environments, typically in the States.

''EG''. ''You could tell from the way he spat old Tupac lyrics, loitering in the corner with his homies, flipping that Yankees cap on his head like he couldn't give a damn, that he was streetwise enough to melt Will Smith''.